hristian-lee-hutson.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/phoebe-bridgers-christian-lee-hutson-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/phoebe-bridgers-christian-lee-hutson-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/phoebe-bridgers-christian-lee-hutson-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/phoebe-bridgers-christian-lee-hutson-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/phoebe-bridgers-christian-lee-hutson-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoebe-bridgers">菲比·布里杰斯 (Phoebe Bridgers)</a>与克里斯蒂安<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/christian-lee-hutson">·李·哈特森 (Christian Lee Hutson)</a>今天（8 月 27 日）在 Connect Festival 上再次登台，此前两人在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-phoebe-bridgers-make-surprise-appearance-christian-lee-hutson-oya-spin-off-show-3481820">本月初的 Øya 音乐节衍生节目中一起表演。</a></p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/boygenius-live-review-setlist-photos-3485875">Boygenius 住在伦敦：脆弱和社区的乌托邦</a></strong></li></ul><p>今天在皇家高地展览场举行的爱丁堡音乐节上， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boygenius">Boygenius</a> （Bridgers 与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/julien-baker">Julien Baker</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lucy-dacus">Lucy Dacus</a>组成的乐队）将成为头条新闻，她与美国乐队一起演唱了《Lose This Number》、《Chesapeake》和《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/christian-lee-hutson-shares-new-single-rubberneckers-with-phoebe-bridgers-3138150">Rubberneckers</a> 》歌手兼作曲家。</p><p>本月早些时候<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-phoebe-bridgers-make-surprise-appearance-christian-lee-hutson-oya-spin-off-show-3481820">，布里杰斯在奥斯陆 Vulkan Arena 音乐厅出人意料地亮相之后，他们的演出也随之而来</a>——赫特森在他正在进行的巡演中成为了该场馆的主角。</p><p>请查看下面本周末表演的片段。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="菲比·布里杰斯 &amp; 克里斯蒂安·李·赫特森" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/h4j_X2yrIaE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="切萨皮克·克里斯蒂安·李·赫特森和菲比·布里杰斯连接音乐节" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SaO6tDQuNvM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="橡皮颈乐队 Christian Lee Hutson 和 Phoebe Bridgers 连接音乐节" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GgR0Kno4N5U?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “菲比和我是这个名为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/better-oblivion-community-center">Better Oblivion Community Center 的</a>乐队的成员，”赫特森在表演《切萨皮克》之前说道。 “我们将从那开始做这首歌，”他说，并开玩笑说他们“可能会中止它”。</p><p>她此前曾与赫特森合作，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/phoebe-bridgers-matty-healy-jack-antonoff-and-more-cover-jackson-browne-these-days-at-ally-coalition-benefit-show-3369506">去年的盟友联盟慈善</a>演出的舞台上以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-phoebe-bridgers-perform-on-cbs-with-christian-lee-hutson-3250455">在哥伦比亚广播公司早间节目的电视节目中</a>合作。她还制作了他的第三张专辑《Beginners》，该专辑于 2020 年发行。</p><p>与此同时，Boygenius 最近在伦敦的 Gunnersbury Park 和哈利法克斯的 The Piece Hall 进行了两场英国演出。</p><p>在上周末的伦敦演出中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-muna-and-boygenius-play-salt-in-the-wound-and-silk-chiffon-at-london-gunnersbury-park-3485850">MUNA 和 Boygenius 联手创作了“Salt In The Wound”和“Silk Chiffon”</a> 。</p><p>两支乐队此前曾在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-muna-bring-out-boygenius-silk-chiffon-at-coachella-2023-3430584">今年早些时候的</a>MUNA<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/coachella">科切拉</a>音乐节上与 Bridgers 合作表演过 MUNA 2021 年单曲“Silk Chiffon”。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoebe-bridgers">菲比·布里杰斯 (Phoebe Bridgers)</a>还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/taylor-swifts-eras-tour-kick-off-top-five-moments-from-the-stars-transcendent-performance-3416005">“Eras”巡演</a>的多场演出中为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift)</a>开场，5 月份的纳什维尔站， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boygenius">Boygenius</a>的其他成员突然出现，令歌迷们大吃一惊。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/boygenius-live-review-setlist-photos-3485875"><em>《NME</em> 》回顾了 Boygenius 上周在伦敦的演出，将这场户外演出描述为“脆弱和社区的乌托邦”</a> 。</p><p>它补充道：“除了他们在歌曲创作和表演方面的才华横溢外，每当其中一位音乐家大声喊出强有力的音符和台词时，就会有一种脆弱感触动你的内心。围绕三人组及其内部也建立了一种社区意识。”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-phoebe-bridgers-make-another-surprise-appearance-with-christian-lee-hutson-at-connect-festival-3489435">观看 Phoebe Bridgers 与 Christian Lee Hutson 在 Connect Festival 上再次惊喜亮相的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
